{"tid":1913703,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE娜璉尺度大開！「床上M字腿」私密處遭看光","createTime":"2020-03-07T04:20:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T06:28:21.000Z","uid":74065,"like":48,"dislike":286,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"739e0a766932ebba49bc9996b55c188c3a86e2d6","tid":1913703,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T04:20:08.000Z","msg":"日前剛結束日本演唱會返回韓國的人氣女團TWICE，因新冠肺炎在韓國持續爆發疫情，讓經紀公司不得不宣布取消首爾場演唱會，台灣成員子瑜更在韓國與大陸兩地捐出善款幫助醫護人員度過難關；而成員娜璉則是在近期受邀拍攝雜誌封面小露性感，同樣吸引網友們討論。<br />\n<br />\n擔任3月號《Cosmopolitan》雜誌封面的娜璉，特別飛到美國換上多套造型展現春天活力，在這幾日釋出的照片中，她除了露出纖細蠻腰外，更換上超激短褲以「M字腿」之姿坐在床上露出嫵媚表情，不少網友看到直呼「又辣又可愛」、「這眼神會殺人」、「身材真是不賴」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SJUkf5X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FSJUkf5X.jpg&h=af0ed3fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SYeDpyM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FSYeDpyM.jpg&h=81c36a08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wzTIeLb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FwzTIeLb.jpg&h=9ad03257&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9TDPdU0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F9TDPdU0.jpg&h=786bab7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Pj81iWP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FPj81iWP.jpg&h=1c86bc88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sBWx2Pz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsBWx2Pz.png&h=4c3a90a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b55012f2d8621682a7178af016cadb7ef275c03e","tid":1913703,"uid":114360,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T04:20:48.000Z","msg":"不知不覺間，今日係梁烈士嘅生忌<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1913659\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1913659</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a180e2a062c536c8063ed588f8cc